snippet.title: The Lands of Eldyn; trailer
snippet.description:
All that remains of Eldyn are warring factions. Will you unite the lands as one or will you venture into its depths to find out what befell these lands? Eldyn is an early release, dark, medieval hack and slash MMO where you conquer territory to gain Valor, unlocking new abilities and powers along the way.

Play for free with no signups at https://eldyn.io

Music by Danheim
